{"tid":2042992,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"男女童涉拋單車堵路被控　13歲男被告申保釋遭拒","createTime":"2020-05-30T06:26:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-30T07:36:41.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"7a9b2799499b6547c7e0d4a7e41cdac9498dea8d","tid":2042992,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T06:26:15.000Z","msg":"政府擬訂立國歌法，周四(28日)惹來大批市民上街抗議，期間兩名男女童涉拋單車等雜物堵路，事後同被控一項在公眾地方造成阻礙罪，今(30日)在粉嶺法院提訊，毋須答辯。裁判官蘇文隆將案押後至8月3日再訊，以待控方索取法律意見，男童還押，女童則獲准保釋。<br />\n<br />\n案中男被告現時13歲，女被告則為12歲。控罪指他們於今年5月28日，在上水馬會道和新運路一帶，用單車、膠欄、雪糕筒和磚頭堵路，造成阻塞。裁判官准女被告保釋，但因男被告有其他案件在身，故駁回其保釋申請。"},{"pid":"63492192e43d513f233fc12aa969c1486ff3c19f","tid":2042992,"uid":328890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T06:26:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2024dd870ba39c06f4ea254fc99438f65d962c44","tid":2042992,"uid":328890,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T06:28:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"aa360b0aac1c5e8b564fb25ed833dee8bda72c90","tid":2042992,"uid":167928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T06:28:56.000Z","msg":"係時候組織連登調查組 查下班紅官背後的利益關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47e40037bba3d2a208b906f19410b5b43a498741","tid":2042992,"uid":183844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T06:29:43.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f1a0e8755960866e317c4bf589c0d76a4073ad6b","tid":2042992,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T06:31:21.000Z","msg":"大家做嘢之前睇清楚情況先，仲有做好保密功夫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c4a6c04d2c236c03334399bb69024e05c7506e9","tid":2042992,"uid":7020,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T06:31:37.000Z","msg":"12歲就要出嚟抗爭<br />\n我12歲嗰陣仲係開開心心打緊機<img src=\"/assets/fac